On the main dashboard (All plans), if I click on a plan, I follow this link :

http://host:8085/browse/PROJECT-PLAN/latest

But this "latest" is problematic for the links build in the page : browse/PROJECT-PLAN/latest because it is used for links in each tab.

Example, for summary tab link, the link is  : {noformat}

